WEBVTT

1
00:16:28.230 --> 00:16:31.570 
云朵这种东西  其实挺靠不住的
Clouds, such as they are, are in fact suspect

2
00:16:31.570 --> 00:16:34.950 
它不同于你抛下的其他东西
and made from a different material than those you left behind.

3
00:16:34.950 --> 00:16:39.410 
你自身就是从一块云布中剪裁而成
You yourself were cut from a different cloudy cloth,

4
00:16:40.470 --> 00:16:41.770 
被退回
returned,

5
00:16:43.110 --> 00:16:44.470 
被剩下
remaindered,

6
00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:47.120 
被月光冷冷洒过
ill-met by moonlight,

7
00:16:47.120 --> 00:16:48.550 
因为回家而郁闷
unhappy to be back,

8
00:16:48.550 --> 00:16:50.860 
在所有不该松散的地方松散
slack in all the wrong spots.

9
00:16:50.860 --> 00:16:52.670 
体面的西装发出阵阵恶臭
Seamy suit of clothes,

10
00:16:52.670 --> 00:16:55.180 
又脏又破
dishrag-ratty, worn.

11
00:16:57.940 --> 00:16:59.480 
你回了家
You return home,

